    "question": "Niederau C, M\u00fcller J, Sonnenberg A, Scholten T, Erckenbrecht J, Fritsch WP et al. Extrahepatic bile ducts in healthy subjects, in patients with cholelithiasis, and in postcholecystectomy patients:",
